snippet.textDisplay: No offense but you don't want people like this in the organization they should remain cheerleaders of their own. I cannot understand a chief that doesn't take accountability and for 15 months cannot make a decision. I would like to scrutinise the recruitment process of SARS  not good. I can do this role with my eyes closed
